headline: VERSANT Board of Directors for Future Independent Media Company Announced
summary: NEW YORK, July 24, 2025--Comcast Corporation (Nasdaq: CMCSA) today announced the expected members of the first Board of Directors of VERSANT Media Group, Inc., Comcast’s planned spin-off of select media brands and digital businesses.
